svg.title: {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}P(r)&=\sum _{i=1}^{n}P\left({\text{applicant }}i{\text{ is selected}}|{\text{applicant }}i{\text{ is the best}}\right)\times P\left({\text{applicant }}i{\text{ is the best}}\right)\\&=\left(\sum _{i=1}^{r-1}0\times {\frac {1}{n}}\right)+\left(\sum _{i=r}^{n}P\left(\left.{\begin{array}{l}{\text{the best of the first }}i-1{\text{ applicants}}\\{\text{is in the first }}r-1{\text{ applicants}}\end{array}}\right|{\text{applicant }}i{\text{ is the best}}\right)\times {\frac {1}{n}}\right)\\&=\sum _{i=r}^{n}{\frac {r-1}{i-1}}\times {\frac {1}{n}}\quad =\quad {\frac {r-1}{n}}\sum _{i=r}^{n}{\frac {1}{i-1}}.\end{aligned}}}
